<BR>
    Anyways, I was wandering around to the bar room in Sol A to get some exp w/ a Lvl27 Cleric, 27 Ranger and a lvl50 warrior (warrior was a friend of mine that came to break the spawn). Well none of us actually knew the way except the lvl27 ranger which lead us down a lil ways until our cleric had to med because of healing us from the constant goblins attacking us around every corner. Well the ranger i guess didn't here him say wait and he took a wrong turn and happened to fall in a pit(hole).When he yelled for help well all ran the way he went and also fell in the hole.When i turned around the ranger was getting pounded by a Reckless Efreeti and 2 Blazing Elementals, we kept him alive for like a half a minute, but unfortunately he died.After his dealth we still had a lil bit of trouble because i had a Blazing Elemental on me and was OOM from healing to ranger. The warrior was on the losing end of the battle also he was nearly dead since the cleric wasn't nearly high enough to heal him more than a bubble of HP per heal and mana was running low.Well we finally defeated them w/ the warrior at one bubble health me at 2 bubbles health the cleric still full and 1 dead ranger. the Blazing Elementals dropped nothing just like the Air elements that we all hated at lvl6 in EC.But the Reckless Efreeti dropped the Platinum Armband which is his common drop(his rare drop is the obsidian scimitar).<BR>
<BR>
    Just thought i tell you an easy way to get the armband if you are prepare to get a beaten.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Lealin Goldenwolf<BR>
